spec_data.Name: python2-mutatormath
spec_data.Description:
MutatorMath is a Python library for the calculation of piecewise linear
interpolations in n-dimensions with any number of masters. It was developed for
interpolating data related to fonts, but if can handle any arithmetic object.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:02:30 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Python library for piecewise linear interpolation in multiple dimensions
